extendedInfo.description: Government Acronym LookupWorks with Android 2.2 (API 8) and higher.)Government Acronym Lookup from CoolFred software is a useful app for anyone who works with or for Government agencies. Select a Data Set and enter an acronym and GAL will tells you what it means.Features:* Search across all of our known agencies or a specific agency* Search for partial acronyms* Select from a list of matching defintions* Information provied: * * Definition* * Dataset* * Date Updated* * Obsolete (Yes / No)* * Verified (Yes / No)* Datasets available* * Department of Transportation (DOT)* * Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI)* * Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA)* * Internal Revenue Service (IRS)* * Stafford Act Titles* * US Army* * Canadian Government * * + more to be addedYou can try Government Acronym Lookup risk free with a trial download.When you are ready to buy, a simple registration code gets you definitions!

reviews.title: Rip-Off
reviews.comment: I can\'t stand a program that advertises itself as free and than has the nerve to charge for it.  It wouldn\'t be so bad if it works but when it only found 3 out of 10 it\'s not worth the download.
reviews.author: A Google User
